SDK
	AWS CLI uses Python SDK (boto3)
	AWS CLI default region is us-east-1
	Credentials by default ~/aws/credentials
	Environment variables can be used for CLI
	exponential backoff - failing API calls wait exponential time

AWS Profiles
	aws configure --profile [profile_name]
	change profile with AWS_DEFAULT_PROFILE env variable